#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.25:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "3. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Mahānāmasutta "
msgstr "25. With Mahānāma "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.25:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, near Kapilavatthu in the Banyan Tree Monastery. "

msgctxt "an8.25:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho mahānāmo sakko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Mahānāma the Sakyan went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.25:1.3"
msgid "“kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, upāsako hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how is a lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.25:1.4"
msgid "“Yato kho, mahānāma, buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti; "
msgstr "“Mahānāma, when you’ve gone for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha, "

msgctxt "an8.25:1.5"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako hotī”ti. "
msgstr "you’re considered to be a lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an8.25:2.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako sīlavā hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how is an ethical lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.25:2.2"
msgid "“Yato kho, mahānāma, upāsako pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti; "
msgstr "“When a lay follower doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence, "

msgctxt "an8.25:2.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako sīlavā hotī”ti. "
msgstr "they’re considered to be an ethical lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.221, sc3
msgctxt "an8.25:3.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako attahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But how do we define a lay follower who is practicing to benefit themselves, not others?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: samādapeti → samādāpeti (?)
msgctxt "an8.25:3.2"
msgid "“Yato kho, mahānāma, upāsako attanāva saddhāsampanno hoti, no paraṃ saddhāsampadāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "“A lay follower is accomplished in faith, but doesn’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.3"
msgid "attanāva sīlasampanno hoti, no paraṃ sīlasampadāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They’re accomplished in ethical conduct, but don’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.4"
msgid "attanāva cāgasampanno hoti, no paraṃ cāgasampadāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They’re accomplished in generosity, but don’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.5"
msgid "attanāva bhikkhūnaṃ dassanakāmo hoti, no paraṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dassane samādapeti; "
msgstr "They like to see the mendicants, but don’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.6"
msgid "attanāva saddhammaṃ sotukāmo hoti, no paraṃ saddhammassavane samādapeti; "
msgstr "They like to hear the true teaching, but don’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.7"
msgid "attanāva sutānaṃ dhammānaṃ dhāraṇajātiko hoti, no paraṃ dhammadhāraṇāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They readily memorize the teachings they’ve heard, but don’t encourage others to do the same. "

# NOTE: BB, PTS, and several manuscripts have dhatanam instead of sutanam, and I correct accordingly.
msgctxt "an8.25:3.8"
msgid "attanāva sutānaṃ dhammānaṃ atthūpaparikkhitā hoti, no paraṃ atthūpaparikkhāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They examine the meaning of the teachings they’ve memorized, but don’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.9"
msgid "attanāva atthamaññāya dhammamaññāya dhammānudhammappaṭipanno hoti, no paraṃ dhammānudhammappaṭipattiyā samādapeti. "
msgstr "Understanding the meaning and the teaching, they practice accordingly, but they don’t encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:3.10"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako attahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāyā”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how we define a lay follower who is practicing to benefit themselves, not others.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.222, sc4
msgctxt "an8.25:4.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako attahitāya ca paṭipanno hoti parahitāya cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But how do we define a lay follower who is practicing to benefit both themselves and others?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.25:4.2"
msgid "“Yato kho, mahānāma, upāsako attanā ca saddhāsampanno hoti, parañca saddhāsampadāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "“A lay follower is accomplished in faith and encourages others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.3"
msgid "attanā ca sīlasampanno hoti, parañca sīlasampadāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They’re accomplished in ethical conduct and encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.4"
msgid "attanā ca cāgasampanno hoti, parañca cāgasampadāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They’re accomplished in generosity and encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.5"
msgid "attanā ca bhikkhūnaṃ dassanakāmo hoti, parañca bhikkhūnaṃ dassane samādapeti; "
msgstr "They like to see the mendicants and encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.6"
msgid "attanā ca saddhammaṃ sotukāmo hoti, parañca saddhammassavane samādapeti; "
msgstr "They like to hear the true teaching and encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.7"
msgid "attanā ca sutānaṃ dhammānaṃ dhāraṇajātiko hoti, parañca dhammadhāraṇāya samādapeti; "
msgstr "They readily memorize the teachings they’ve heard and encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.8"
msgid "attanā ca sutānaṃ dhammānaṃ atthūpaparikkhitā hoti, parañca atthūpaparikkhāya samādapeti, "
msgstr "They examine the meaning of the teachings they’ve memorized and encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.9"
msgid "attanā ca atthamaññāya dhammamaññāya dhammānudhammappaṭipanno hoti, parañca dhammānudhammappaṭipattiyā samādapeti. "
msgstr "Understanding the meaning and the teaching, they practice accordingly and they encourage others to do the same. "

msgctxt "an8.25:4.10"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako attahitāya ca paṭipanno hoti parahitāya cā”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how we define a lay follower who is practicing to benefit both themselves and others.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.25:4.11"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

